[Name] XDG-User-Dirs
[Summary] Manage XDG user directories.
[Description] Xdg-user-dirs is a tool to help manage "well known" user
directories like the desktop folder and the music folder. It also
handles localization (i.e. translation) of the filenames.
[License] GPL v2.0
[Homepage] https://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/xdg-user-dirs
